<!DOCTYPE html>
<html style="overflow-y: hidden;">
<head>
	<title></title>
</head>
<body style="height: auto; min-height: auto;">
<div style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333;">
<p>Dear Manager,</p>

<p>An expense sheet has been submitted for your review and approval for the following project:</p>

<div style="margin-left: 20px; border-left: 3px solid #0176d3; padding-left: 15px;">
<p><strong>Project Name:</strong> {ProjectName}<br />
<strong>Submitted By:</strong> {SubmitterName}<br />
<strong>Total Amount:</strong> <span style="color: #2e844a; font-weight: bold;">{GrandTotal}</span></p>
</div>

<p>Please review the attached PDF report and the original bill image for details. To take action on this request, please click the button below:</p>

<p style="margin-top: 25px;"><a href="{ApprovalLink}" style="background-color: #0176d3; color: #ffffff; padding: 12px 25px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 4px; font-weight: bold; display: inline-block;">Review and Authorize </a></p>

<p style="margin-top: 30px; font-size: 12px; color: #777;">Best Regards,<br />
<strong>Arelia Living&nbsp;</strong></p>
</div>
</body>
</html>